    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      77.29,
      415.03,
      90.57
    ],
    "text": "Cannabis Cultivation Raided; Suspect Arrested \u2013 Athimale Police",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      105.13,
      516.75,
      159.69
    ],
    "text": "Acting on information received in the early hours of 09.03.2026, a team of officers from the Police Narcotics Bureau, together with officers from the Athimale Police Station, conducted a raid in the protected area of Kebiliththa, Kotiyagala, within the Athimale Police Division.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      174.25,
      511.54,
      215.13
    ],
    "text": "During the operation, officers discovered and seized 55,220 cannabis plants that had been cultivated across an area of approximately two acres. The plants had grown to a height of nearly six feet and ten inches.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      229.69,
      515.38,
      270.6
    ],
    "text": "A suspect has been taken into custody in connection with the illegal cultivation of the cannabis plantation and has been produced before the Athimale Police Station for further legal proceedings.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      285.04,
      385.03,
      298.32
    ],
    "text": "The suspect is a 34-year-old resident of the Embilipitiya area.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
